trans-unit.source: Initializes the associated <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.CorrelationInitializer.CorrelationHandle*> with a callback correlation.
trans-unit.target: 初始化相關聯<xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.CorrelationInitializer.CorrelationHandle*>與回呼相互關聯。</xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.CorrelationInitializer.CorrelationHandle*>

trans-unit.source: A callback correlation is based on the callback context exchange mechanism described in the [.NET Context Exchange Protocol Specification](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=163882).
trans-unit.target: 回呼相互關聯根據所述的回呼內容交換機制[.NET 內容交換通訊協定規格](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=163882)。

trans-unit.source: To use callback correlation, a context-based binding such as <xref:System.ServiceModel.BasicHttpContextBinding>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpContextBinding>, or <xref:System.ServiceModel.NetTcpContextBinding> must be used.
trans-unit.target: 若要使用回呼相互關聯，以內容為主的繫結這類<xref:System.ServiceModel.BasicHttpContextBinding>， <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpContextBinding>，或<xref:System.ServiceModel.NetTcpContextBinding>必須使用。</xref:System.ServiceModel.NetTcpContextBinding> </xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpContextBinding> </xref:System.ServiceModel.BasicHttpContextBinding>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.CallbackCorrelationInitializer"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.CallbackCorrelationInitializer"></xref>類別。
